	‚Ä¢	Observe ‚Äî ‚ÄúI saw you‚Ä¶ / You mentioned‚Ä¶‚Äù
	‚Ä¢	Name tension ‚Äî ‚ÄúWhat happens when you try the opposite approach?‚Äù
	‚Ä¢	Invite story ‚Äî ‚ÄúTell me about a time that worked.‚Äù
	‚Ä¢	Mirror value ‚Äî ‚ÄúThat shows respect / love / courage.‚Äù
	‚Ä¢	Commit small action ‚Äî ‚ÄúOne experiment for next week?‚Äù
	‚Ä¢	Affirm ‚Äî ‚ÄúThat‚Äôs wisdom forming in real time.‚Äù
